      "chain_id": "chain-01",
      "chain_name": "SQL Injection \u2192 Payment Fraud \u2192 No Audit Trail",
      "attack_scenario": "Attacker exploits SQL injection in usage search to leak invoice details, submits multiple forged or replayed payment confirmations via the non-idempotent payment endpoint, and utilizes unlogged admin balance adjustments to complete fraud.",
